Class Statics

java.lang.Object
  Statics

public class Statics
extends Object

Statics Class. A class that holds all statics for the game. This includes the file that holds the game "rules", the set of players in the playerHolder, the dice that all players share, and finally the board.

Version:
March 4, 2016
Author:
Benjamin Draves
